FBIS4-20999 "jptdd014__l94059" JPRS-TDD-94-014-L JPRS Narcotics 26 March 1994 EAST ASIA VIETNAM Opium Burned, Confiscated in Yen Bai Province Opium Burned, Confiscated in Yen Bai Province BK2703123694 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 1430 GMT 26 Mar 94 BK2703123694 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network Vietnamese BFN [Text] The Yen Bai provincial people's committee recently burned 38 kg of confiscated opium at the 19 May Square in Yen Bai City. This is the fourth time the province has destroyed a large volume of opium since its implementation of the government's program on preventing and opposing drug addiction. While striving to destroy opium, the province has actively detected and arrested those who engage in drug trafficking. Recently, the province monitored and arrested the driver of a car with 43.7 kg of opium.
